reviewText: REALLY LAME, EVEN FOR A B MOVIE.

Boring. For a bike film to succeed, in my opinion, it has to have at least a little bit of drama. Just showing bikes and listening to regular-guy interviews is dull. Living the bike life is better than watching folks talking about it.
My hometown excellent video of the week

Don't waste your time or money on this "Mickey Mouse" video, it is poor quality and has nothing but clip shots from other Sturgis films pasted together in a real crap hodgepodge.  There are far better videos out there to be seen on the subject of Sturgis, this one is a total waste of your time and money!
